high_descs: turn into kitchen, walk to face stove
pick up tea kettle from stove top
walk right to face kitchen sink
place kettle into left sink basin, wash, pick up kettle
walk right to face counter top above dish washer
place kettle on counter top below two brass vases
anns.task_desc: place a washed kettle on a kitchen counter top

high_descs: Turn around and move to the stove.
Pick up the kettle from the back right corner of the stove.
Carry the kettle to the sink, which is to your right.
Place the kettle in the left side of the sink, turn the water on, and then remove once it has been washed.
Carry the kettle to the coffee maker, which is just a little right of the sink.
Place the kettle on the counter to the left of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed kettle by the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the stove to the far right.
Pick up the kettle on the stove.
Carrying the kettle, walk to the sink to your left.
Place the  kettle in the sink, wash it, then remove the kettle.
Carrying the clean kettle, walk to the coffee maker to your left.
Place the clean kettle on the counter where the coffee maker is.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean kettle on the counter.
